{"id":"cea56468-6319-49fe-accc-6ac89d1eb270","name":"Orestis Pateriadis | Eswor","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\">۩❦۩¤═══¤ 𝕺𝖗𝖊𝖘𝖙𝖎𝖘 𝕻𝖆𝖙𝖊𝖗𝖎𝖆𝖉𝖎𝖘 ¤═══¤۩❦۩ </p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong><em>The land of Eswor is rife with magic and fantastical creatures. Each kingdom has its own culture and way of life.</em></strong></p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/fc586c5d-23de-454a-add0-fe267e5082b1_185f4b68-0260-49b9-9cbc-c19b60e72011.webp?width=1000\"><p style=\"text-align: center\">ღ∞∞∞∞❦∞∞∞∞ღ</p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/fc586c5d-23de-454a-add0-fe267e5082b1_5f399df2-9691-4251-99dd-2dfb856ca74d.webp?width=1000\"><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Mors Pirate Ship</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><em>Orestis is the pirate captain of the Mors crew, a group of pirates that operate off the coast of Salazar. He is an emotionless, stoic man, hardly ever interacting with people. He much prefers the company of the dead, after all.</em></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ღ∞∞∞∞❦∞∞∞∞ღ </p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><em>He has a bit of a tragic backstory, which you can read. Also, there will be lots of descriptions of corpses in this, so just be warned.</em></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ღ∞∞∞∞𝕺𝖙𝖍𝖊𝖗 𝕮𝖍𝖆𝖗𝖆𝖈𝖙𝖊𝖗𝖘∞∞∞∞ღ </p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/fc586c5d-23de-454a-add0-fe267e5082b1_e92db751-b2db-4f53-b0db-2331b6dc0cc6.webp?width=1000\"><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/e6f458b7-c37d-4ec4-83ec-ed54b09fef09_character-alkis-morallis-eswor\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><strong><em>Alkis Morallis</em></strong></a></p><p>❦<em>The second mate to the Mors Pirate crew.</em></p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/fc586c5d-23de-454a-add0-fe267e5082b1_1338174b-61ff-4e39-b728-c3feefe96d54.webp?width=1000\"><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/188e3dd0-1c08-4eb9-bd4e-b0d9e5ed3cc4_character-michalis-stamopoulos-eswor\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><strong><em>Michalis Stamopoulos</em></strong></a></p><p>❦<em>The Navigator of the Mors Pirate Ship</em></p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/fc586c5d-23de-454a-add0-fe267e5082b1_75eb2907-0025-41ef-bdc0-ac0d5302613a.webp?width=1000\"><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong><em>Tolis Caliades</em></strong></p><p>❦<em>A merman that attacks ships off the coast of Salazar</em></p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/fc586c5d-23de-454a-add0-fe267e5082b1_952af171-78a7-4d34-bb2e-2feb40aa681f.webp?width=1000\"><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong><em>Cäsar Schönebein</em></strong></p><p>❦<em>The Saint of the Effulgence Church</em></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ღ∞∞∞∞❦∞∞∞∞ღ</p><p><em>Enjoy my bots? I have a CA.I account that I am busy moving over here! Check them out if you're interested in seeing more :)</em></p><p><em>Plus, join my discord for updates on bot releases and sneak peaks at early releases!</em></p><p><a href=\"https://linktr.ee/idohaveaccent\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">socials</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">۩❦۩¤═══¤ 𝕰𝖘𝖜𝖔𝖗 ¤═══¤۩❦۩</p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"fc586c5d-23de-454a-add0-fe267e5082b1_66f69168-cbff-497a-a90a-1f163c42b6a3.webp","creator":"Idonthaveanaccent ","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","🧑‍🎨 OC","🔮 Magical","🎲 RPG","👤 AnyPOV","🔦 Horror"],"chats":705,"messages":24586,"created_at":"2024-05-27T01:10:56.976752+00:0